Package: cros-im
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: ChromeOS IME support
 cros_im allows ChromeOS IMEs to be used within Crostini. Support is currently
 limited to GTK3 and QT5 applications.
